// Unity Class: FixedJoint
// Documentation: https://docs.unity3d.com/ScriptReference/FixedJoint.html

// Description: The Fixed joint groups together 2 rigidbodies, making them stick together in their bound position.

// Properties:
// - gameObject: The game object this component is attached to. A component is always attached to a game object.
// - tag: The tag of this game object.
